Package org.apache.juneau.bean.openapi3

Class Parameter

java.lang.Object
org.apache.juneau.bean.openapi3.OpenApiElement
org.apache.juneau.bean.openapi3.Parameter
@Bean(properties="name,in,description,required,deprecated,allowEmptyValue,style,explode,allowReserved,schema,example,examples,*") public class Parameter extends OpenApiElement
Describes a single operation parameter.
